# Summary
The Anomaly + Forecast feature in Amplitude identifies statistically significant deviations in metrics based on historical data, using Prophet forecasting methodology with three modes (agile, robust, custom) and configurable confidence intervals, helping teams distinguish meaningful fluctuations from noise and project future metric values.

